# CFBagGetTypeID()

**Function**

Returns the type identifier for the CFBag opaque type.

## Declaration

```swift
func CFBagGetTypeID() -> CFTypeID
```

## Return Value

The type identifier for the CFBag opaque type.

## Discussion

CFMutableBag objects have the same type identifier as CFBag objects.
